text: Herbert MacPherson (20 February 1869 - 12 November 1953) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1893/94 and 1894/95. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1869 births Category:1953 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: Herbert MacPherson (cricketer)
